channel.title: Bracket (}) Problem
channel.description:
I added a code then compiled and I got this error:
[code]server.java:262: reached end of file while parsing } ^ 1 error Compiler worked Successfully! Press any key to continue . . . [/code]
I'm not positive, but I think the "262" is line 262. It's just a bracket:
[img]http://www.imgjoe.com/x/bracketprob.png[/img]
(Numbers on left side are the line numbers.)

item.title: Bracket (}) Problem
item.dc:creator: @The_Web_Guy The Web Guy
item.description:
@The_Web_Guy wrote:

It’s not a balanced equation, you’re missing a bracket somewhere, an end bracket. This error simply means that when compiling the file, the compiler couldn’t find the end of the file. Adding a bracket to the end may fix your problem, if it doesn’t, go through and find where to put the bracket, in the correct place.
